rComments: He's my favorite ECE professor by a long shot. He moves fast through lecture, but only so he can try to give you as much info as possible. Incredible at explaining things in a comprehensible way. He's an entertaining lecturer, and always tries to make himself available to his students
This guy is one of better 340 professors. Speaks very clearly and quite helpful. A lot of the material is dry but he makes little jokes and class activities to make it interesting.

Wasserman is a godsend to the ECE department. He teaches very effectively, making very complicated concepts relatively easy to understand. He's also quite funny and sarcastic. Initially, he was not my lecturer, but I switched into his lecture and a sea of understanding washed over me. If you can, definitely go to his class.
